title: @@GORGEOUS 3/2 with Garage, Huge Yard, Two Level Deck!!
posting_body: ['GORGEOUS 3/2 with Garage, Huge Yard, Two Level Deck, Stainless Appliances, Washer/Dryer & More!', '$1250/month Avail June 20 You will love this update at home that features a two car garage, hard surface flooring throughout (no carpet), granite COUNTERTOPS, Stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, walk-in closet, and a BEAUTIFUL two level deck.', 'Washer and dryer included.', 'Enjoy the massive yard and BEAUTIFUL landscaping without worrying about the mowing, lawn MAINTENANCE is included.', 'This home is perfect for those looking for a place tucked away in, but also great for entertaining.', 'Excellent location close to Capital Circle Northeast, TENNESSEE St., and downtown.', 'Showings start June 20th.', '*Renters insurance required.', '*Cats and small dogs only, no ANIMALS over 30 pounds.', 'Pet fee is $100, REFUNDABLE.', 'PLEASE CALL FOR MORE INFORMATION', 'show contact info']
